{"coursehistories": {"path": "/coursehistories/3382"}, "description": "The student will learn to conceptualize and produce animation design ideas with an eye on the possibility of making the art of animation a future career. The student will be introduced to the workings of hand-drawn digital 2D animation design using a Wacom tablet and software TVPaint, specializing in this type of production. Emphasis will be placed on: 1) the development of drawing skills particularly related to the creation of paperless animation in a quick and effortless style: 2) the finesse of representing a sense of drama and motion within a single frame; 3) storytelling skills fulfilling a mission of urgency and purposefulness; 4) the pursuit of originality in a world where almost everything has already been done. Students are required to buy their own Wacom Intuos2 pens. \n\n", "semester": "2011C", "name": "HAND-DRAWN COMPUTER ANIM", "reviews": {"path": "/courses/24397/reviews", "values": [{"ratings": {"rAmountLearned": "3.00", "rDifficulty": "2.40", "rStimulateInterest": "2.60", "rRecommendMajor": "3.60", "rCourseQuality": "2.80", "rWorkRequired": "3.40", "rInstructorAccess": "2.40", "rReadingsValue": "2.00", "rRecommendNonMajor": "2.20", "rCommAbility": "3.00", "rInstructorQuality": "2.20"}, "section": {"name": "HAND-DRAWN COMPUTER ANIM", "sectionnum": "401", "primary_alias": "FNAR-241-401", "path": "/courses/24397/sections/401", "id": "24397-401", "aliases": ["FNAR-241-401", "FNAR-541-401"]}, "comments": "", "num_students": 10, "path": "/courses/24397/sections/401/reviews/2480-PAUL-S--FIERLINGER", "instructor": {"path": "/instructors/2480-PAUL-S--FIERLINGER", "first_name": "PAUL S.", "last_name": "FIERLINGER", "id": "2480-PAUL-S--FIERLINGER", "name": "PAUL S. FIERLINGER"}, "num_reviewers": 5, "id": "24397-401-2480-PAUL-S--FIERLINGER"}, {"ratings": {"rAmountLearned": "3.00", "rDifficulty": "2.40", "rStimulateInterest": "3.20", "rRecommendMajor": "3.60", "rCourseQuality": "2.80", "rWorkRe